With the African Mining Indaba currently taking place in Cape Town, Classic Business Breakfast with Moneyweb talks to Nivaash Singh, head of mining and resources finance international at Nedbank CIB, about the sustainability of mining in South Africa and the the rest of the world. Singh gives insight into challenges facing banks doing business on the African continent in the sector. <a href="https://iono.fm/e/651596">Content hosted by iono.fm</a> Read: Changing the narrative around SA mining Africa’s long-term mining potential